# Prometheus 接入开发计划

本文档描述接入 Prometheus 监控后，系统的完整故障处理流程。

---

## 一、Prometheus 接入概述

### 1.1 配置参数

```python
@dataclass
class PrometheusConfig:
    # 连接配置
    base_url: str = "http://localhost:9090"

    # 认证方式
    auth_type: Literal["none", "bearer", "basic", "mtls"] = "none"
    token: str | None = None
    username: str | None = None
    password: str | None = None
    tls_cert: str | None = None
    tls_key: str | None = None

    # 查询配置
    timeout: int = 30
    max_retries: int = 3

    # 告警配置
    alertmanager_url: str | None = None
```

### 1.2 依赖

```bash
# requirements.txt 添加
httpx>=0.25.0
prometheus-api-client>=0.19.0
```

